# Customer app, auth, and AI

Read **CLAUDE.md** app flows and **agents.md** auth and AI sections.

## Customer app

- Slug-based multi-tenant entry from App.tsx URL routing
- Reel UX: vertical scroll, watch sessions, cart, checkout
- Hard cap on dishes shown in reel — product requirement
- Separate customer auth (sign-up, OTP, profile) from owner Supabase session

## Owner login

Google OAuth and email/password via Supabase; redirect URL uses VITE_SITE_URL in production.

## AI (geminiService)

Anthropic Claude behind legacy filename. Pinned model for cost/speed. Missing API key or API failure → friendly fallback string, never uncaught throw to UI. New AI features follow the same guard pattern as existing functions in that module.

## Types

Shared interfaces in types.ts — extend there before inline types in components.
